|GKB-- Whirlwind -------------------------------------------------|000

By using the Tekali current, the druid can bind a
wind spirit to create a whirlwind around an
opponent, battering and disorienting them.
The enemy must use some of its strength to
fight the whirlwind, leaving it less able
to battle the druid.

|CKBCommand:      |000 whirlwind <target> (defaults to attacker)
|CKBBase Cost:    |000 40 Tekali nwyfre
|CKBBase Recovery:|000 medium
|CKBBase Effect:  |000 drain (strength, moderate), damage (low)
|CKBBase Duration:|000 medium
|CKBGuild Level:  |000 6
